  "text": "make an export of ComponentPublicInstanceConstructor type into runtime-core.d.ts\n\n### What problem does this feature solve?\n\nour team use this type to declare component props and we have to use patch for that\n\n### What does the proposed API look like?\n\n-declare type ComponentPublicInstanceConstructor\r\n+export declare type ComponentPublicInstanceConstructor",
